  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     GAN
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Generator vs discriminator adversarial training
Year:        2014
Researchers: Ian Goodfellow et al.
Applications:Image synthesis, deepfakes, augmentation
Related:     Mode collapse, discriminator, generator

Concept:     Transformer
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Attention-based model processing sequences in parallel
Year:        2017
Researchers: Vaswani et al.
Applications:LLMs, vision models, protein folding
Related:     GPT, BERT, attention mechanism

Concept:     RLHF
Category:    Training technique
Definition:  Fine-tunes LLMs using human preference comparisons
Year:        2017
Researchers: Christiano et al.
Applications:ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini alignment
Related:     PPO, reward model, preference learning

